<a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/jocelyne-de-nicola/" title="View all posts by Jocelyne De Nicola" rel="author">Jocelyne De Nicola</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/alexandre-duhamel/" rel="tag">Alexandre Duhamel</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/beatrice-uria-monzon/" rel="tag">Batrice Uria Monzon</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/clementine-margaine/" rel="tag">Clmentine Margaine</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gregory-warren/" rel="tag">Gregory Warren</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/hector-berlioz/" rel="tag">Hector Berlioz</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lawrence-foster/" rel="tag">Lawrence Foster</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/les-troyens/" rel="tag">Les Troyens</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marc-barrard/" rel="tag">Marc Barrard</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marie-kalinine/" rel="tag">Marie Kalinine</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/nicolas-courjal/" rel="tag">Nicolas Courjal</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-di-marsiglia/" rel="tag">Opra di Marsiglia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roberto-alagna/" rel="tag">Roberto Alagna</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alexandre Duhamel, Batrice Uria Monzon, Clmentine Margaine, Gregory Warren, Hector Berlioz, Lawrence Foster, Les Troyens, Marc Barrard, Marie Kalinine, Nicolas Courjal, Opra di Marsiglia, Roberto Alagna"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b3247e7dbc632a4b9e79d7e45fbef703" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Jocelyne-De-Nicola-130x200.jpg" width="65" height="100" alt="Jocelyne De Nicola" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Jocelyne De Nicola"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/jocelyne-de-nicola/">View all articles by Jocelyne De Nicola</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/07/roma-soiree-roland-petit/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Roma: Soire Roland Petit</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/07/macerata-opera-festival-2013nabucco/" rel="next">Macerata, Opera Festival 2013:&#8221;Nabucco&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/07/marsiglia-opera-municipal-les-troyens/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'55778\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_parent\' id=\'comment_parent\' value=\'0\' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="2619132238" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak_js" name="ak_js" value="92"/></p></form></div></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;Baccanali&#8221; di Agostino Steffani\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1903-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Baccanali, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;Baccanali&#8221; di Agostino Steffani" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1903-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1903-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/i-due-foscari-al-teatro-real-di-madrid-con-placido-domingo/\' title=\'I due Foscari al Teatro Real di Madrid con Plcido Domingo\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Angela Meade, Placido Domingo, Michael Fabiano" title="I due Foscari al Teatro Real di Madrid con Plcido Domingo" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Madrid-Teatro-Real-18-VII-2016-I-Due-Foscari-5-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(max-width: 70px) 100vw, 70px" /></a></li><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg 70w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-75x75.jpg 75w" sizes="(